title: Nav N Go iGO 8 for Samsung i900 SD
description:
Nav N Go iGO 8 for Samsung i900 SD.

This is my personal edition.

This includes maps 2008.Q3_081204 for Europe, USA, Russia and Ukraine.

Software version - Nav N Go iGO 8.3.2.64029 - November, 7th, 2008.

1. Extract IGO_8_SD.rar on your PC.

2. Copy 2577 and iGO8 folders on MicroSD (Storage Card/2577; Storage Card/iGO8)

3. Run the autorun.exe file from 'Storage Card/2577' folder (not from your PC).

Follow the prompts accepting all of them.

Default COM port - '0' (Check your Samsung i900 GPS setting)


Dobrogo puti :)
